### Backend

- Database: `DB_HOST`, `DB_PORT`, `DB_USER`, `DB_PASSWORD`, `DB_NAME`, `DB_SSL_MODE`
- JWT: `JWT_ACCESS_SECRET`, `JWT_REFRESH_SECRET`, `JWT_ACCESS_EXPIRATION`, `JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRATION`
- OAuth: `GITHUB_*`, `GOOGLE_*`, `OAUTH_STATE_SECRET`, `FRONTEND_URL`
- AI: `OPENAI_API_KEY`, `OPENAI_MODEL_NAME`, `OPENAI_BASE_URL`
- Server: `SERVER_PORT`, `SERVER_HOST`, `ENV`

### Frontend

- `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL`

Keep secrets out of VCS. Full context in [CLAUDE.md](mdc:CLAUDE.md).
